# FixedIntegral - Bundle protocol for fixed-width integer operations
# Extends Integral with Invertible (bitwise NOT) and overflow handling
module Core

protocol FixedIntegral follows Integral, Invertible, OverflowAddable, OverflowSubtractable, OverflowMultiplicable, OverflowExponentiable, CheckedDivisible, CheckedShiftable {
    pass
}
